WhosHere 5 – With this release, a completely redesigned and improved user experience is brought to WhosHere! The introduction of a side menu enables users to navigate WhosHere features in a fraction of the time. Whether you are looking for friendship or love, enjoy an enhanced user experience with our unique features, including, picture sharing and real time communication with your privacy still intact!

WhosHere - The original social discovery app.

WhosHere Voice' in app calling has been fixed. Call other WhosHere users without disclosing your phone number!

- Improved chat experience. See when someone is typing a reply to you.

- More ways to earn WhosHere points for free.

- Bug fixes.

We have optimized the application's performance for a smoother user experience.  Over 8 million awesome people use WhosHere every day to make friends, socialize, chat, date, exchange photos, flirt, find their love interests, and get found by people they like. Most of them are based in the US, the Middle East, and Europe; so if you’re in these regions, WhosHere is your best bet.
